quran[9{c,v,t}:
2,49,"yaad karo woh waqt, jab hum ne tum ko firounion ki ghulami se nijaat bakhsh onhon ne tumhe sakht azaab mein mubtala kar rakha tha, tumahray larkoon ko zibah karte thay aur tumhari larkiyon ko zindah rehne dete thay aur is haalat mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumhari barri azmaish thi"
2,50,"yaad karo woh waqt, jab hum ne samandar phaar kar tumahray liye rasta banaya, phir is mein se tumhe bakhariat guzaar diya, phir wahein tumhari aankhon ke samnay fironoon ko garqaab kiya"
2,51,"yaad karo, jab hum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ko chalees Shabana roz ki qarardad par bulaya, to is ke peechay tum bichhre ko apna mabood bana baithy uss waqt tum ne barri zayad-ti ki thi"
2,52,magar is par bhi Hum ne tumhe maaf kar diya ke shayad ab tum shukar guzaar bano
2,53,yaad karo ke ( theek is waqt jab tum yeh zulm kar rahay thay ) hum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ko kitaab aur Farqan ataa ki taakay tum is ke zariye se seedha rasta pasko
2,54,"yaad karo jab( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)( yeh Nemat letay hue palta, to uss ) ne apni qoum se kaha ke"" logo, tum ne bachhre ko mabood bana kar apne oopar sakht zulm kya hai, lehaza tum log apne khaaliq ke huzoor tauba karo aur apni jaanun ko halaak karo, isi mein tumahray khaaliq ke nazdeek tumhari behtari hai"" uss waqt tumahray khaaliq ne tumhari tauba qubool kar li ke woh bara maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
2,55,"yaad karo jab tum ne( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)se kaha tha ke hum tumahray kehnay ka hargiz yaqeen nah karen ge, jab taq ke apni aankhon se alania khuda ko ( tum se kalaam karte ) nah dekh lain is waqt tumahray dekhte dekhte aik zabardast saiqayne tum ko aa liya"
2,56,"tum bay- jaan ho kar gir chuke thay, magar phir hum ne tum ko(zindah kardiya) jِlaa uthaya, shayad ke is ahsaan ke baad tum shukar guzaar ban jao"
2,57,"hum ne tum par abr ka saya kya, mann-o-salwa ki ghiza tumahray liye faraham ki aur tum se kaha ke jo pak cheeze hum ne tumhe bakhshi hain, unhen khao, magar tumahray islaaf ne jo kuch kya, woh hum par zulm nah tha, balkay unhon ne aap apne hi aap par zulm kya"
